thread.title_full: Alaska Northern Lights reviewed by EMILY BALDWIN

author: EMILY BALDWIN
title: EMILY BALDWIN
text: The product is actually effective! I definitely feel like I have increased energy and the symptoms of SAD are all but gone! I chose this supplier for the design of their product (sleek, modern, simple) and the fact that they had readily available forms for submitting an insurance claim to cover the cost of the therapy box. Fast delivery and an all-around great experience. Fully satisfied!
